                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2018-20796**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| low  | libc-bin  | 2.42-16  |   | deb  | /var/lib/dpkg/status  | debian:distro:debian:unstable  | [CVE-2018-20796](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2018-20796)  |\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "purls": [
                  "pkg:deb/debian/libc-bin@2.42-16?arch=amd64\u0026distro=debian\u0026upstream=glibc"
                ],
                "security-severity": "7.5"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CVE-2018-20796-libc-gconv-modules-extra",
              "name": "DpkgMatcherExactIndirectMatch",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2018-20796 low vulnerability for libc-gconv-modules-extra package"
