              "helpUri": "https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2022-0563",
              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2022-0563\nSeverity: low\nPackage: libsmartcols1\nVersion: 2.42.1-3\nFix Version: \nType: deb\nLocation: /var/lib/dpkg/status\nData Namespace: debian:distro:debian:unstable\nLink: [CVE-2022-0563](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2022-0563)",
